Response: { "file_id": "crisis_comm_plan_v1.docx", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/d4f5g-hjk", "collaborators": [{ "email": "pr_director@corp.com", "permission": "comment" }] }

Question: Downgrade the vendor's access from edit to view-only for the supply chain database effective immediately.
Call: { "func_call": "revoke_access", "file_id": "supply_chain_db_export.sql", "user_email": "vendor_logistics@supplychain.io", "permission": "view", "expires_at": "2024-12-12T10:30:00Z" }
